{"title":"午晌","authors":["白曙"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":10,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"午晌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白曙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"初夏的骄阳挂在晴空上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大巷里落下片白光；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"架上葡萄对微风打盹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸽儿在檐边也睡得够香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只这伙孩子野马到处跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手上还握着杆“卡宾枪”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侦察偷袭像群小兵丁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弄巷给闹成个大战场。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢善战打趟出色的仗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“冲呀”！大伙喊个震天价晌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随着开大炮——扔石头瓦片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎顾得着什么玻璃窗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳台上有人摇摇手说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“喂！你们别吵那么大声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁家的孩儿不受管教？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是我家宝宝正睡午晌。”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}